It is the 53rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|ๅญๅๅนฒๆฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Yin Wood Rabbit|ja|1=Yin Wood Rabbit|2=ja|ไนๅฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rabbit|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Yang Fire Snake|ja|1=Yin Fire Snake|2=ja|ไธๅทณ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Snake|qq=}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|้ฐ้ฝไบ่กๆๆณ|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|ๅๅนฒ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Yang Fire|ja|ไธ|1=Hinoe (ไธ)|lt=Hinoe (ไธ)|2=ja|3=ไธ|4=zh|5=ไธ|1=Hinoe (ไธ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (ไธ)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|็ซ|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (็ซ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|ๅไบๆฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Dragon|ja|่พฐ|1=Dragon (Zodiac)|lt=Dragon (่พฐ)|2=ja|3=่พฐ|1=Dragon (zodiac)|lt=Dragon (่พฐ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Dragon (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|ๅ|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (ๅ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|ไบ่กๆๆณ#็ธ็๏ผใใใใใ๏ผ|lt=Mutual Generation|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) (็ซ็ๅ).

