'''Yang Fire Dragon also known as ไธ่พฐ''' (hinoetatsu, heikano-tatsu, heishin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|ๅญๅๅนฒๆฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 53rd combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|ๅญๅๅนฒๆฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Yin Wood Rabbit|ja|1=Yin Wood Rabbit|2=ja|ไนๅฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rabbit|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rabbit|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rabbit|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Yang Fire Snake|ja|1=Yin Fire Snake|2=ja|ไธๅทณ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Snake|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Snake|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Snake|qq=}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|้ฐ้ฝไบ่กๆๆณ|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|ๅๅนฒ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Yang Fire|ja|ไธ|1=Hinoe (ไธ)|lt=Hinoe (ไธ)|2=ja|3=ไธ|4=zh|5=ไธ|1=Hinoe (ไธ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (ไธ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (ไธ)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|Fire (็ซ)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (็ซ)|2=uk|3=ะะพะณะพะฝั (ะฃ-ััะฝ)|4=bcl|5=Kalayo (wuxing)|6=pt|7=Fogo (astrologia)|8=vi|9=Hแปa (Ngลฉ hร nh)|10=ar|11=ุงููุงุฑ (ูู ุดููุบ)|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (็ซ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire (wuxing)|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|ๅไบๆฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Dragon|ja|่พฐ|1=Dragon (Zodiac)|lt=Dragon (่พฐ)|2=ja|3=่พฐ|1=Dragon (zodiac)|lt=Dragon (่พฐ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Dragon (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Dragon (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (ๅ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (ๅ)|2=ru|3=ะะตะผะปั (ั-ัะธะฝ)|4=mn|5=ะจะพัะพะพ (ะผะฐัะฑะพะด)|6=uk|7=ะะตะผะปั (ะฃ-ััะฝ)|8=als|9=รrde in dr chinesische Fรผmf-Elemรคnt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thแป (Ngลฉ hร nh)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (ๅ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|ไบ่กๆๆณ#็ธ็๏ผใใใใใ๏ผ|lt=Mutual Generation|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) (็ซ็ๅ).

