'''Yang Fire Dragon also known as ไธ่พฐ''' (hinoetatsu, heikano-tatsu, heishin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|ๅญๅๅนฒๆฏ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

