==Yang Fire Dragon (ไธ่พฐ)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|่ฅฟๆฆ|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=่ฅฟๆฆ|4=zh|5=ๅฌๅ|6=es|7=Era comรบn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|ๅๅนฒ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|็ธ|1=Mizunoto (็ธ)|lt=Mizunoto (็ธ)|2=ja|3=็ธ|4=zh|5=็ธ|1=Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|ๆ|1=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|lt=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|2=ja|3=ๆ|4=zh|5=ๆ|1=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3ๆ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March|qq=}} is designated as the month of {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=}}. However, here the term โmonthโ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ๆงๆฆ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|็ฏๆ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=|12=sim