==Pronunciation== ==Years of Yang Fire Dragon== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that, when divided by 60, leaves a remainder of 56 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yang Fire Dragon (ไธ่พฐ)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 56|56 AD]] * [[:en:AD 116|116 AD]] * [[:en:176|176 AD]] * [[:en:236|236 AD]] * [[:en:296|296 AD]] * [[:en:356|356 AD]] * [[:en:416|416 AD]] * [[:en:476|476 AD]] * [[:en:536|536 AD]] * [[:en:596|596 AD]] * [[:en:656|656 AD]] * [[:en:716|716 AD]] * [[:en:776|776 AD]] * [[:en:836|836 AD]] * [[:en:896|896 AD]] * [[:en:956|956 AD]] | * [[:en:1016|1016 AD]] * [[:en:1076|1076 AD]] * [[:en:1136|1136 AD]] * [[:en:1196|1196 AD]] * [[:en:1256|1256 AD]] * [[:en:1316|1316 AD]] * [[:en:1376|1376 AD]] * [[:en:1436|1436 AD]] * [[:en:1496|1496 AD]] * [[:en:1556|1556 AD]] * [[:en:1616|1616 AD]] * [[:en:1676|1676 AD]] * [[:en:1736|1736 AD]] * [[:en:1796|1796 AD]] * [[:en:1856|1856 AD]] * [[:en:1916|1916 AD]] * [[:en:1976|1976 AD]] | * {{ill|2036 AD|ja|2036ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2036|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2036 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2096 AD|ja|2096ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2096|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2096 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2156 AD|ja|2156ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2156|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2156 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2216 AD|ja|2216ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2216|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2216 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2276 AD|ja|2276ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2276|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2276 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2336 AD|ja|2336ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2336|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2336 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2396 AD|ja|2396ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2396|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2396 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2456 AD|ja|2456ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2456|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2456 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2516 AD|ja|2516ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2516|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2516 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2576 AD|ja|2576ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2576|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2576 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2636 AD|ja|2636ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2636|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2636 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2696 AD|ja|2696ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2696|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2696 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2756 AD|ja|2756ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2756|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2756 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2816 AD|ja|2816ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2816|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2816 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2876 AD|ja|2876ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2876|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2876 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2936 AD|ja|2936ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2936|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2936 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2996 AD|ja|2996ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2996|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2996 AD|qq=}} |} ==Months of Yang Fire Dragon== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Gui|ja|็ธ|1=Mizunoto (็ธ)|lt=Mizunoto (็ธ)|2=ja|3=็ธ|4=zh|5=็ธ|1=Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|ๆ|1=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|lt=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|2=ja|3=ๆ|4=zh|5=ๆ|1=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:March|March]] is designated as the month of {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=}}. However, here the term โmonthโ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ๆงๆฆ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Qingming (solar term)|Qingming]] until the day before [[:en:Lixia|Lixia]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Fire Dragon== ==={{nihongo|selection days|้ธๆฅ|senjitsu|qq=}}=== The selected day for {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=}} is the gap day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|ๅ ซๅฐ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}.
