ed day for {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} is the gap day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|ๅ ซๅฐ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}.
