|13=User:Immanuelle/2876|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2876 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2936 AD|ja|2936ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2936|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2936 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2996 AD|ja|2996ๅนด|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2996|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2996 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |} ==Months of Yang Fire Dragon== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Gui|ja|็ธ|1=Mizunoto (็ธ)|lt=Mizunoto (็ธ)|2=ja|3=็ธ|4=zh|5=็ธ|1=Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (็ธ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|ๆ|1=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|lt=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|2=ja|3=ๆ|4=zh|5=ๆ|1=Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (ๆ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:March|March]] is designated as the month of {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. However, here the term โmonthโ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ๆงๆฆ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Qingming (solar term)|Qingming]] until the day before [[:en:Lixia|Lixia]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Fire Dragon== ==={{nihongo|selection days|้ธๆฅ|senjitsu|qq=}}=== The selected day for {{ill|Yang Fire Dragon|ja|1=Yang Fire Dragon|2=ja|ไธ่พฐ|1=Yang Fire Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Dragon|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} is the gap day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|ๅ ซๅฐ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}.
